{"id":"the-wandering-seed-cart","slug":"the-wandering-seed-cart","title":"The Wandering Seed Cart","title_ko":"떠돌이 씨앗 수레","level":"A2","ageBand":"8-10","coverUrl":"/seed/the-wandering-seed-cart/cover.webp","summary_ko":"씨앗 수레가 마을 곳곳을 지나며 사람들에게 알맞은 씨앗을 나누는 이야기예요.","wordCount":110,"pages":[{"id":"the-wandering-seed-cart-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/the-wandering-seed-cart/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-wandering-seed-cart-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"A wooden cart of seeds rolled into our town on a windy day.","translation_ko":"바람 부는 날 씨앗 수레가 우리 마을로 굴러 들어왔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-wandering-seed-cart/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"A","charStart":0,"charEnd":1,"startMs":0,"endMs":180},{"word":"wooden","charStart":2,"charEnd":8,"startMs":180,"endMs":460},{"word":"cart","charStart":9,"charEnd":13,"startMs":460,"endMs":840},{"word":"of","charStart":14,"charEnd":16,"startMs":840,"endMs":1080},{"word":"seeds","charStart":17,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1080,"endMs":1420},{"word":"rolled","charStart":23,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1420,"endMs":1960},{"word":"into","charStart":30,"charEnd":34,"startMs":1960,"endMs":2200},{"word":"our","charStart":35,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2200,"endMs":2400},{"word":"town","charStart":39,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2400,"endMs":2680},{"word":"on","charStart":44,"charEnd":46,"startMs":2680,"endMs":2880},{"word":"a","charStart":47,"charEnd":48,"startMs":2880,"endMs":3040},{"word":"windy","charStart":49,"charEnd":54,"startMs":3040,"endMs":3280},{"word":"day","charStart":55,"charEnd":58,"startMs":3280,"endMs":3620}]}]},{"id":"the-wandering-seed-cart-p2","pageNo":2,"spread":"p2","imageUrl":"/seed/the-wandering-seed-cart/p2.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-wandering-seed-cart-p2-s1","ord":0,"text":"No one pushed it, but its little wheels knew the road.","translation_ko":"아무도 밀지 않았지만 작은 바퀴들은 길을 알고 있었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-wandering-seed-cart/audio/p2-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"No","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":660},{"wo